Note that this is not the same problem as the Year 2038 problem.

NTP was calculating seconds since Jan 1st 1900 with an unsigned 32-bit integer (fails in February 2036). 

time_t was calculating seconds since Jan 1st 1970 with a signed 32-bit integer (fails in January 2038).
